{"id":120,"name":"战争之影","alias":"Hecarim","title":"赫卡里姆","shortBio":"赫卡里姆是人与兽的幽灵混合体，身上的诅咒让他只能永世不停地践踏生者的灵魂。在福光岛被暗影吞噬之际，这位高傲的骑士被破败之咒的毁灭能量彻底湮没——连同他的骑兵团和他们胯下的坐骑。现在，符文之地上只要是有黑雾出现的地方，就会有赫卡里姆率军冲锋的鬼影，他们肆虐雀跃，用铁蹄践踏着脚下的幽魂。","isVisibleInClient":true,"tacticalInfo":{"style":7,"difficulty":2,"damageType":"kPhysical","attackType":"melee"},"playstyleInfo":{"damage":2,"durability":2,"crowdControl":2,"mobility":2,"utility":1},"championTagInfo":{"championTagPrimary":"机动","championTagSecondary":"陷阵"},"squarePortraitPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/v1/champion-icons/120.png","stingerSfxPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/v1/champion-sfx-audios/120.ogg","chooseVoPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/v1/champion-choose-vo/120.ogg","banVoPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/v1/champion-ban-vo/120.ogg","roles":["fighter","tank"],"recommendedItemDefaults":[],"skins":[{"id":120000,"contentId":"2d5c237b-4650-4d5d-892e-e7822ea2fa1f","isBase":true,"name":"战争之影","skinClassification":"kChampion","splashPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Hecarim/Skins/Base/Images/hecarim_splash_centered_0.jpg","uncenteredSplashPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Hecarim/Skins/Base/Images/hecarim_splash_uncentered_0.jpg","tilePath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Hecarim/Skins/Base/Images/hecarim_splash_tile_0.jpg","loadScreenPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Hecarim/Skins/Base/HecarimLoadscreen_0.jpg","skinType":"","rarity":"kNoRarity","isLegacy":false,"splashVideoPath":null,"previewVideoUrl":null,"collectionSplashVideoPath":null,"collectionCardHoverVideoPath":null,"featuresText":null,"chromaPath":null,"emblems":null,"regionRarityId":0,"rarityGemPath":null,"skinLines":null,"description":null},{"id":120001,"contentId":"337399aa-a591-41f5-b6db-952102554991","isBase":false,"name":"血石骑士 赫卡里姆","skinClassification":"kChampion","splashPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Hecarim/Skins/Skin01/Images/hecarim_splash_centered_1.jpg","uncenteredSplashPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Hecarim/Skins/Skin01/Images/hecarim_splash_uncentered_1.jpg","tilePath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Hecarim/Skins/Skin01/Images/hecarim_splash_tile_1.jpg","loadScreenPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Hecarim/Skins/Skin01/HecarimLoadScreen_1.jpg","skinType":"","rarity":"kNoRarity","isLegacy":false,"splashVideoPath":null,"previewVideoUrl":null,"collectionSplashVideoPath":null,"collectionCardHoverVideoPath":null,"featuresText":null,"chromaPath":null,"emblems":null,"regionRarityId":0,"rarityGemPath":null,"skinLines":[{"id":126}],"description":"赫卡里姆对他的教团来说是一个狂热的谄媚者，总是毫不迟疑地服侍着血石的意志。虽然没有他的主人们想要的那么精巧，但他在以可怕的方式处决敌人们时总是非常有效率。"},{"id":120002,"contentId":"ae7a3ce6-a72d-4f1e-bbe1-d3b9e7eb3f33","isBase":false,"name":"幽魂骑士 赫卡里姆","skinClassification":"kChampion","splashPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Hecarim/Skins/Skin02/Images/hecarim_splash_centered_2.jpg","uncenteredSplashPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Hecarim/Skins/Skin02/Images/hecarim_splash_uncentered_2.jpg","tilePath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Hecarim/Skins/Skin02/Images/hecarim_splash_tile_2.jpg","loadScreenPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Hecarim/Skins/Skin02/HecarimLoadScreen_2.jpg","skinType":"","rarity":"kNoRarity","isLegacy":false,"splashVideoPath":null,"previewVideoUrl":null,"collectionSplashVideoPath":null,"collectionCardHoverVideoPath":null,"featuresText":null,"chromaPath":null,"emblems":null,"regionRarityId":0,"rarityGemPath":null,"skinLines":[{"id":87}],"description":"每当死者拒绝接受死亡誓约给予他们的一席之地时，幽魂骑士赫卡里姆就会用他早已准备好的镰刀送他们一程。在他身后充斥着无数被征服的鬼魂，现在赫卡里姆只渴望收获新鲜并具挑衅性的灵魂。"},{"id":120003,"contentId":"88ff45e1-afeb-48d0-9c5e-3a237bedc4fe","isBase":false,"name":"无头骑士 赫卡里姆","skinClassification":"kChampion","splashPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Hecarim/Skins/Skin03/Images/hecarim_splash_centered_3.jpg","uncenteredSplashPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Hecarim/Skins/Skin03/Images/hecarim_splash_uncentered_3.jpg","tilePath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Hecarim/Skins/Skin03/Images/hecarim_splash_tile_3.jpg","loadScreenPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Hecarim/Skins/Skin03/HecarimLoadScreen_3.jpg","skinType":"","rarity":"kNoRarity","isLegacy":true,"splashVideoPath":null,"previewVideoUrl":null,"collectionSplashVideoPath":null,"collectionCardHoverVideoPath":null,"featuresText":null,"chromaPath":null,"emblems":[{"name":"Halloween_b","emblemPath":{"large":"/lol-game-data/assets/v1/emblem-images/11.png","small":"/lol-game-data/assets/v1/emblem-images/11.png"},"positions":{}}],"regionRarityId":7,"rarityGemPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/v1/rarity-gem-icons/7_large.png","skinLines":[{"id":88}],"description":"关于夜晚在路间徘徊的生物有着诸多故事，但没有一个会像无头骑士的故事那般黑暗。他在一场马背对决中失去了自己的头颅，这注定了他的生活永远被困扰-他的肩头只能扛着一个丑陋的杰克南瓜灯。"},{"id":120004,"contentId":"4b6f4993-a510-4b74-97b4-09d3d91023d0","isBase":false,"name":"电玩战魂 赫卡里姆","skinClassification":"kChampion","splashPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Hecarim/Skins/Skin04/Images/hecarim_splash_centered_4.jpg","uncenteredSplashPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Hecarim/Skins/Skin04/Images/hecarim_splash_uncentered_4.jpg","tilePath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Hecarim/Skins/Skin04/Images/hecarim_splash_tile_4.jpg","loadScreenPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Hecarim/Skins/Skin04/HecarimLoadScreen_4.jpg","skinType":"","rarity":"kEpic","isLegacy":true,"splashVideoPath":null,"previewVideoUrl":null,"collectionSplashVideoPath":null,"collectionCardHoverVideoPath":null,"featuresText":null,"chromaPath":null,"emblems":[{"name":"Limited","emblemPath":{"large":"/lol-game-data/assets/v1/emblem-images/1.png","small":"/lol-game-data/assets/v1/emblem-images/1.png"},"positions":{}}],"regionRarityId":7,"rarityGemPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/v1/rarity-gem-icons/7_large.png","skinLines":[{"id":10}],"description":"他似乎很难成为复古游戏中的最爱人选，但是赫卡里姆确实是街机时代最受欢迎的人气角色。他现在要对抗由游戏内最危险的反派组成的大军，证明自己才是自从1978年以来最伟大的带着彩虹尾巴的半人马。"},{"id":120005,"contentId":"f2bd01d6-870e-4442-9e89-351ecd77177e","isBase":false,"name":"永恒之森 赫卡里姆","skinClassification":"kChampion","splashPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Hecarim/Skins/Skin05/Images/hecarim_splash_centered_5.jpg","uncenteredSplashPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Hecarim/Skins/Skin05/Images/hecarim_splash_uncentered_5.jpg","tilePath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Hecarim/Skins/Skin05/Images/hecarim_splash_tile_5.jpg","loadScreenPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Hecarim/Skins/Skin05/HecarimLoadScreen_5.jpg","skinType":"","rarity":"kEpic","isLegacy":false,"splashVideoPath":null,"previewVideoUrl":null,"collectionSplashVideoPath":null,"collectionCardHoverVideoPath":null,"featuresText":null,"chromaPath":null,"emblems":[{"name":"Epic","emblemPath":{"large":"/lol-game-data/assets/v1/emblem-images/29.png","small":"/lol-game-data/assets/v1/emblem-images/29.png"},"positions":{}}],"regionRarityId":4,"rarityGemPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/v1/rarity-gem-icons/4_large.png","skinLines":[{"id":58}],"description":"他所穿的是夏木和花楸轻纺而成的护甲——他身上的石头雕刻于一段时光，那时古神们尚未在树丛之中起舞。即使是现在，赫卡里姆仍在永恒之森里浅浅的河流和点缀着青苔的小路中旅行着，这个不老的守护者保护着森林，抵抗着人类那最为黑暗的众多渴求。"},{"id":120006,"contentId":"b313e4e8-fa52-4020-bc23-b271188caa83","isBase":false,"name":"创世之神 赫卡里姆","skinClassification":"kChampion","splashPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Hecarim/Skins/Skin06/Images/hecarim_splash_centered_6.jpg","uncenteredSplashPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Hecarim/Skins/Skin06/Images/hecarim_splash_uncentered_6.jpg","tilePath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Hecarim/Skins/Skin06/Images/hecarim_splash_tile_6.jpg","loadScreenPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Hecarim/Skins/Skin06/HecarimLoadscreen_6.jpg","skinType":"","rarity":"kNoRarity","isLegacy":false,"splashVideoPath":null,"previewVideoUrl":null,"collectionSplashVideoPath":null,"collectionCardHoverVideoPath":null,"featuresText":null,"chromaPath":null,"emblems":null,"regionRarityId":0,"rari